cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and natural language inference. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural machine translation systems and training classifiers. Additionally, it may be relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of neural networks, and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as some NMT systems incorporate visual information.
